cs.CV, cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG 

This paper is about color normalization in digital pathology, which involves image processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of GPU-acceleration and deep learning libraries, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.DL (Machine Learning) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses algorithmic improvements and speedup techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
